{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-054","title":"Sentence 54","sectionId":"sentences-051","sectionTitle":"Sentence 51-60","pageStart":358,"pageEnd":362,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":19,"duplicateEntryCount":13,"pages":[{"number":358,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 54"},{"type":"text","text":"The jaw joints of many advanced herbivores, such as cows, lie at a"},{"type":"text","text":"different level than the tooth row, allowing transverse tearing, shredding,"},{"type":"text","text":"and compression of plant material."},{"type":"text","text":"许多高级食草动物——比如牛——的颌关节和牙排位于不同的"},{"type":"text","text":"水平面上，这样可以横向撕裂、切碎、压缩植物材料。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句主干是The jaw joints lie at a different level than the tooth"},{"type":"text","text":"row。“allowing ... plant material”是非谓语结构作伴随状语，其中"},{"type":"text","text":"tearing、shredding和compression作allowing的并列宾语。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"jaw /dʒɔː/ n. 颌，颚","headword":"jaw"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 “嚼”→他下颌脱臼了，没法嚼东西→颌"},{"type":"entry","text":"advanced /ədˈvænst/ a. 先进的；高级的","headword":"advanced"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 join（结合，连接）+t→关节"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 advanced technology先进的技术"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 advance v. 发展；前进"}]},{"number":359,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"herbivore /ˈhɜːrbɪvɔːr/ n. 食草动物","headword":"herbivore"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 herbi（=herb草）＋vor（吃）＋ous（…的）→食草的"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 scavenger n. 食腐动物"},{"type":"text","text":"omnivore n. 杂食动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"transverse /ˈtrænzvɜːrs/ a. 横向的","headword":"transverse"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 transverse section横切面"},{"type":"entry","text":"shred /ʃred/ vt. 切碎，撕碎n. 碎片","headword":"shred"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 shredder n. 切碎机"},{"type":"entry","text":"compression /kəmˈpreʃn/ n. 压缩，浓缩","headword":"compression"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 compress v. 压缩"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“